# Speech Enhancement Project Rules

## Project Overview

This project is a research project on speech enhancement.
The main goals are:
1. To estimate the clean speech from the noisy speech.

## Virtual Environment Usage

When executing commands in the terminal, always activate the environment first:
```bash
# if using MP-SENet
source ./.venv/mp_senet_env/bin/activate
# if using SEMamba++
source ./.venv/se_mamba_pp_env/bin/activate
```
